    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195990/extras/dfc856bbd4e3c9386bbbbbf923badb61.avif?t=1771789124\" width=780 height=189 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rhyolite answers the oft-wondered question &quot;What if <i>Ghostbusters</i> was set on a railway in the Wild West?&quot; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >YOUR OBJECTIVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive each battle</strong> until you have enough data about the enemy ghost train to CAPTURE IT.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195990/extras/c4c39434915687b01f4a72ecee36b535.poster.avif?t=1771789124\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195990/extras/c4c39434915687b01f4a72ecee36b535.webm?t=1771789124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE CHAOTIC COMBAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Think on your feet</strong> to handle ghostly attacks that randomly lock doors, swap players, and misplace items. The chaos is real!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195990/extras/26bffb48f88aea0002de963ee04b53d4.poster.avif?t=1771789124\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195990/extras/26bffb48f88aea0002de963ee04b53d4.webm?t=1771789124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ROGUELITE VARIETY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a different combination of enemy attacks, curses, and train upgrades, <strong>every run is totally unique!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195990/extras/eb7f46a2db619b145e0cefc4ba7166ec.poster.avif?t=1771789124\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195990/extras/eb7f46a2db619b145e0cefc4ba7166ec.webm?t=1771789124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack by Josie Brechner</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 4 players online co-op</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging single player mode, with help from Frank the Automaton </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
